<h2 style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;">各学院</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;">:</span><br/></h2><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">为进一步做好校友工作，搭建毕业生与母校沟通桥梁，加强毕业生走向社会后与母校及校友会的联系，及时掌握校友信息，促进母校和校友事业的共同发展，经学校研究决定，在</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">届毕业生中选拔校友工作</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">联络员</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">，现将有关事项通知如下：</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">一、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">选聘范围</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">202</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">届毕业生以班级为单位推荐，每个班级</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">1名。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">二、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">基本条件</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">思想品德端正，关心母校事业，关注母校发展</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">热心校友工作，具有奉献精神和服务意识</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">交际、组织能力及责任心强。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">群众基础及综合素质好，在同学中有较高号召力和凝聚力，能积极组织班级同学开展活动。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">5、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">在学期间担任学生干部的同学优先。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">三、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">主要职责</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">保持与学校和本班同学的联系，掌握同学动态，协助学校健全、更新校友信息，及时向学校校友</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">办</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">反馈。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">积极参加校友会、校友分会活动及校友分会筹建工作，组织开展本班校友活动。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">收集本班同学对学校的意见和建议并及时反馈，支持学校建设发展。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">积极向校友</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">办</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">推荐优秀校友事迹供学校宣传报道。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">四、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">校友联络员享有的服务</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">优先参加各地校友分会活动。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">优先了解母校、校友会和校友的相关信息。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">优先参加校友会举办的各种联谊、培训和交流活动。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">学校向校友联络员颁发聘书。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">五、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">选任办法及程序</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">1、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">采用个人自荐与学院推荐相结合的方式进行。学生向所在学院自荐，也可由学院根据对学生的了解情况，并经学生本人同意，推荐优秀学生担任校友联络员，校友</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">办</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">统一颁发聘书。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 27px"><span style="font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">2、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">各学院选拔结束确认汇总后，统一发送至校友</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">联络</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">办公室。</span></p><p style="margin-left: 0;text-indent: 27px"><span style="font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">六、</span><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">工作要求</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">各学院请于</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">9</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">26</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">日前将《</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2024</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">届校友工作联络员汇总表》</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">《</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">联络员</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">推荐表</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">》</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">纸质版报送校友</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">联络</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">办公室</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">(IBM楼101办公室）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">备案，并将电子版发送至邮箱</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">804532064@qq.com</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">邮件标题：学院名称</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">+202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">4</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">届毕业班校友工作联络员。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">联系人：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">徐元斌</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋">电话：</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">17607912375</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">附件一：江西软件职业技术大学</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2024</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">届校友工作联络员汇总表</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">附件二：江西软件职业技术大学校友联络员推荐表</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 43px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:336px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">江西软件职业技术大学</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:336px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">校友联络办公室</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:336px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">202</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">9</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">21</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">日</span></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;" src="/resource/js/ueditor-1.4.3.3/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_txt.gif"/><a style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/data/upload/img/20231010/1696920589776091748.xlsx" title="江西软件职业技术大学2024届毕业班校友联络员汇总表.xlsx">江西软件职业技术大学2024届毕业班校友联络员汇总表.xlsx</a></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 2px;" src="/resource/js/ueditor-1.4.3.3/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif"/><a style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" href="/data/upload/img/20231010/1696920589830095194.docx" title="江西软件职业技术大学校友联络员推荐表.docx">江西软件职业技术大学校友联络员推荐表.docx</a></p><p><br/></p>